                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    sling:resourceType="core-components-examples/components/text"
                    text="&lt;p>For structured content fragments, it is possible to limit the output to certain elements in the data. In this example we again show the same office, but only its &lt;i>title&lt;/i> and&lt;i> city&lt;/i>.&lt;/p>"
